        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>37 cloud regions on AWS and Azure where frontier model providers route inference traffic. Toggle between grid carbon intensity (Ember 2025) and baseline water stress (WRI Aqueduct 4.0). Two regions (Hong Kong, Singapore) lack water-stress scores due to Aqueduct&apos;s hydrological-basin methodology — flagged in the tooltip when in water-stress view.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
